{"tid":640282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擬元朗明渠上建高架行人路　接駁朗屏站至教育路　路政署料斥17.85億元","createTime":"2018-04-24T07:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T08:32:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f348e088c8497b94a0f613c92a847da5bb0cb6a8","tid":640282,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180423/s00001/7aea2b2ae515ff9090f3573de29bc43e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180423%2Fs00001%2F7aea2b2ae515ff9090f3573de29bc43e.jpg&h=7dd0f0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180423/s00001/7aedd646d3cc2c25f9308c2a1dd76a2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180423%2Fs00001%2F7aedd646d3cc2c25f9308c2a1dd76a2e.jpg&h=f7c2c86f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工程構思圖。（路政署）<br />\n<br />\n立法會交通事務委員會，即將開會討論路政署建議，在元朗明渠上興建一段高架行人通道，連接朗屏西鐵站至教育路以南。根據署方提交立法會的討論文件，項目旨在分流市中心地面人流，從而紓緩擠迫情況和提升道路安全，估算工程費用為17.85億元。<br />\n<br />\n路政署表示，元朗市中心安寧路、青山公路和教育路一帶，行人活動頻繁，可是街道狹窄，路人有時擠出行車道，構成潛在交通安全問題。擬建工程包括一條有蓋高架行人通道，長約540米、闊6米，沿路將設6個接駁平台，有樓梯、升降機和自動梯，連接行人通道和路面（見圖1及圖2），建成後有望改善擠迫問題。<br />\n<br />\n討論文件未有提及施工需時長短，只稱其間將有臨時交通安排，經評估後「不會對該區交通網絡造成重大的影響」。署方並稱，曾在2010年、2011年及2013年，就有關工程分別諮詢過區議會、立法會及公眾等，結果獲得普遍支持。<br />\n<br />\n交通事務委員會會議將在星期五（27）召開。當日與會者亦會討論在葵涌青山公路至工業街，興建升降機及行人通道系統，期望可便利市民往返石籬區及工業街一帶，預計工程費用約為5.844億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180423/s00001/1524490536959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180423%2Fs00001%2F1524490536959&d=dwnxjq7AAAmXthCMTWeEyk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=975b00f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180423%2Fs00001%2F1524490536959&h=cdba29f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180423/s00001/1524490536959</a>"},{"pid":"d9a47a08c55b897d11713dd4060fa7c3f6f45d19","tid":640282,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"終於同班牛屎佬傾掂數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e0b9ba9e236c5691b173bf5d91bf09eafc92b0","tid":640282,"uid":38671,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"17.85億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家元朗起條路都報咁大數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d45d761dc6f5ff1c57d044a8bf5e6d9196cf903","tid":640282,"uid":52459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:30:46.000Z","msg":"一定有陰謀"},{"pid":"afee608b2a6aa9ef6eb158adcb5fd9a3d54732fe","tid":640282,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9a47a08c55b897d11713dd4060fa7c3f6f45d19","tid":640282,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"終於同班牛屎佬傾掂數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"純粹係市區起條高架路<br />\n應該唔關牛屎佬事？"},{"pid":"491a6b284221f95650a1971b28bd9385b2dc2104","tid":640282,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afee608b2a6aa9ef6eb158adcb5fd9a3d54732fe","tid":640282,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9a47a08c55b897d11713dd4060fa7c3f6f45d19","tid":640282,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"終於同班牛屎佬傾掂數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"純粹係市區起條高架路<br />\n應該唔關牛屎佬事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:33:30.000Z","msg":"幾年前CCTVB有講過呢單野，當時唔知係邊班人阻頭阻勢起唔成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" cl